    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s finally time for someone else to get behind the wheel. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been totally pampered, garage-kept, and is basically flawless inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions or come by to see it for yourself\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
