    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This example is mechanically superlative, with documented rod bearing replacement and a proactively reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throw, delivering power through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension has been meticulously maintained with OEM bushings to preserve the original turn-in characteristics and steering feedback. Finished in original Carbon Black metallic, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior remains free of bolster wear or UV damage. A turn-key specimen for the serious purist.",
