    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that retains its deep, showroom luster with absolutely zero chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Every body panel is original, and the factory paint depth remains consistent throughout. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, while the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. All electronics, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It features a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is spotless, the transmission shifts with factory-new precision, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or debris. This is a collector-grade example suited for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
